		<li id="ERP">
    <p class="MsoNormal">The District is currently seeking proposals for the implementation of a new Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) software system. We have engaged with expert consultants to guide us through this process. Interested vendors are invited to thoroughly review the provided RFP documentation. As part of your submission, please complete the accompanying response spreadsheet, which will aid us in evaluating your proposal effectively. We look forward to receiving detailed proposals that address our specific needs and requirements as outlined in the RFP.<br> <b>Deadline to submit bids is 5:00 PM on Wednesday, January 26, 2024.</b><br>
    <br>
    <a href="https://ww2.valleyair.org/media/adaj0mgs/sjv-erp-solution-rfp.pdf?v=20231218.1">
    Request for Proposal - Enterprise Resource Planning Solution</a><br>
    <a href="https://ww2.valleyair.org/media/bgxhsqt3/sjv-erp-rfp-appendix-1-system-requirements.xlsx?v=20231218.1">
    Appendix 1 - System Requirements</a><br>
    <a href="https://ww2.valleyair.org/media/d35hrgyw/sjv-erp-rfp-appendix-2-total-cost-of-ownership.xlsx?v=20231218.3">
    Appendix 2 - Total Cost of Ownership</a><br>
&nbsp;</p>
    
    </li>



